{"tid":1767833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Trump 特朗普：不急於與中國達協議　待明年總統大選後更好","createTime":"2019-12-03T15:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T15:35:44.000Z","uid":125193,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4df67ae37438e8a33e4e3e4ad69085d3dd8a0a","tid":1767833,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:05:19.000Z","msg":"中美首階段貿易談判陷入停滯之際，到英國倫敦準備出席北約峰會的美國總統特朗普突然表示，不急於與中國達成協議，等到明年總統大選後會更好。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，特朗普的說法，顯示美國不惜將中美貿易談判變成一場持久戰，可能令貿易談判的前景增添更多不明朗因素。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮高級顧問康韋較早時就說，雙方仍然有望在年底前達成首階段貿易協議，目前正在敲定協議文本。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">美國商務部長羅斯警告，如果在本月15日美方對中國商品加徵關稅期限前，談判仍沒有進展，美國將如期向1560億美元的中國貨，加徵15%的關稅。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495817-20191203.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495817-20191203.htm&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=268db387\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495817-20191203.htm&h=37b111e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495817-20191203.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2320f3bcf1c0f3ceb8d5231d375499d22976e51f","tid":1767833,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6915f94d5202ced40df68af9283b2c0b1049a544","tid":1767833,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fd8786eb4eb832e1250b7955af19247ff4b991","tid":1767833,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"撐警証據"},{"pid":"7247b26dae620f9ec444285f9747694ad6ddb456","tid":1767833,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}